WEBVTT

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:35.400
Growing up, I played hockey
until I was 12 years old.

00:03:36.880 --> 00:03:39.576
The older I got, the more I felt

00:03:39.600 --> 00:03:42.976
it was harder to keep up
with everyone else,

00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:46.040
and I was angry and frustrated.

00:03:47.800 --> 00:03:51.296
For a while, I did not play any sports,

00:03:51.320 --> 00:03:53.216
didn't have many friends

00:03:53.240 --> 00:03:56.000
and felt left out and sad.

00:03:58.080 --> 00:04:02.496
There was a time when people
